# Mantra4Change API examples (REST Client / VS Code / Cursor)
# Requires server on :4000, analytics on :8000, seeded MongoDB

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@analyticsUrl = http://localhost:8000
@month = 2025-09
@grantId = GRANT_AA_2025

### Health � basic
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Health � full (Mongo, analytics, AI status)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health/full

### Meta � CSV seed preview counts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/meta/seed-preview

### Program � filter options
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/program/filters

### Program � dashboard KPIs + MoM
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/program/dashboard?month={{month}}

### Program � dashboard with district filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/program/dashboard?month={{month}}&district=District T

### Program � district performance table
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/program/districts?month={{month}}

### Program � block performance table
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/program/blocks?month={{month}}

### Program � risk analysis
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/program/risks?month={{month}}

### Program � review summary (legacy structured lists)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/program/review-summary?month={{month}}

### Program � monthly review (Tier 2 leadership brief)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/program/monthly-review?month={{month}}

### Program � recommended actions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/program/action-items?month={{month}}

### Program � regenerate actions
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/program/action-items/regenerate?month={{month}}

### Program � update action status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/program/action-items/2025-09----improve-evidence-rate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in_progress"
}

### Grants � catalog
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/grants

### Grants � facts for grant/month
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/grants/{{grantId}}/{{month}}/facts

### Grants � deterministic report
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/grants/{{grantId}}/{{month}}/report

### Charts � program trends (Plotly JSON)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/charts/program-trends
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "month": "{{month}}",
  "exportPng": false
}

### Charts � district performance with PNG export
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/charts/district-performance
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "month": "{{month}}",
  "exportPng": true
}

### Charts � risk distribution
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/charts/risk-distribution
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "month": "{{month}}",
  "exportPng": false
}

### Charts � grant utilization
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/charts/grant-utilization
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "grantId": "{{grantId}}",
  "month": "{{month}}",
  "exportPng": false
}

### Program report
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/program
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "month": "{{month}}",
  "aiRequested": true
}

### Grant report
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/grant
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "grantId": "{{grantId}}",
  "month": "{{month}}",
  "aiRequested": true
}

### Evidence static image
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/student_project_activity_photo_01.png

# --- Python analytics service (direct) ---

### Analytics health
GET {{analyticsUrl}}/health

### Pandas dashboard (parity reference)
GET {{analyticsUrl}}/analytics/program/dashboard?month={{month}}

### Cross-check Node vs pandas
POST {{analyticsUrl}}/analytics/verify-dashboard
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "month": "{{month}}"
}

### Data quality report
GET {{analyticsUrl}}/analytics/data-quality
